  <brief_title>Evaluate the Efficacy of the Treatment of Iatrogenic Subcutaneous Abdominal Wounds (ISAW) After Surgery by Application of Negative Pressure Wound Therapy (NPWT) in Comparison to Standard Conventional Wound Therapy (SCWT) of the Clinical Routine</brief_title>
  <acronym>ISAW</acronym>
  <official_title>Randomised Controlled Study to Evaluate the Efficacy of the Treatment of Iatrogenic Subcutaneous Abdominal Wounds (ISAW) After Surgery by Application of Negative Pressure Wound Therapy (NPWT) in Comparison to Standard Conventional Wound Therapy (SCWT) of the Clinical Routine.</official_title>
